---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="TacticalPilot | Onboarding & Workflow Automation CRM"
  description="Standardize every new hire and keep an audit trail of tasks, approvals and evidence. Company activation, end-to-end."
  lang="en"
>
  <Fragment slot="logo">TacticalPilot</Fragment>
  <Fragment slot="footer-name">TacticalPilot</Fragment>

  <section class="hero">
    <h1>TacticalPilot</h1>
    <p class="tagline">Company Activation, End-to-End</p>
    <p>Standardize every new hire and keep an audit trail of tasks, approvals and evidence.</p>
  </section>

  <div class="ad-slot">Ad Space - Google AdSense</div>

  <div class="card-grid">
    <article class="card">
      <h2>Onboarding Workflow</h2>
      <p>Managers define required steps (email, tools, access, documents). Role-specific checklists for email setup, device allocation, security protocols, documentation, and location-specific requirements.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h2>Guided Workspace</h2>
      <p>Employees complete steps in a guided private workspace. Each step is tracked with status, notes, and evidence.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h2>CRM Routing</h2>
      <p>Customer requests routed to appropriate staff with SLA, status tracking, notes, and complete audit documentation.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h2>Permissions & Groups</h2>
      <p>Permission assignment at group or individual levels. Permissions automatically trigger associated tasks and approval processes.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h2>Country-Aware</h2>
      <p>Supports region-specific operational variations and localized procedures for international teams.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h2>Multilingual</h2>
      <p>Employees view content in their language while management receives unified reporting.</p>
    </article>
  </div>

  <div class="ad-slot">Ad Space - Google AdSense</div>

  <section class="registration-info">
    <h2>Contact & Registration</h2>
    <p><strong>Email:</strong> info@tacticalpilot.org</p>
    <p><strong>Status:</strong> Live - Invite Only Beta</p>
    <p><strong>Location:</strong> Noregon - London (KI)</p>
    <p><strong>License:</strong> KBN-40-000003 (KIFA)</p>
  </section>

  <div class="ad-slot">Ad Space - Google AdSense</div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .tagline {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    opacity: 1;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .registration-info {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 32px;
    margin-top: 32px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    text-align: center;
  }
  .registration-info h2 {
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    color: #1a1a2e;
  }
  .registration-info p {
    margin: 6px 0;
    color: #555;
  }
</style>
